        <div class="row">
                <div class="small-12 small-centered columns">
                        <div class="story">
                                <h3>
                                    <a href="https://www.thenation.com/article/after-i-lived-in-norway-america-felt-backward-heres-why/">
                                    After I Lived in Norway, America Felt Backward. Here’s Why.                                    </a>
                                </h3>
                                <h5>A crash course in social democracy.</h5>
                                <a class="author" href="https://www.thenation.com/authors/ann-jones/">Ann Jones</a>                                <hr>                                
                                <p>
                                Some years ago, I faced up to the futility of reporting truths about America’s disastrous wars, and so I left Afghanistan for another mountainous country far away. It was the polar opposite of Afghanistan: a peaceful, prosperous land where nearly everybody seemed to enjoy a good life, on the job&hellip;                                       
